<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>You've been invited to join <strong><%= SiteSetting.app_name %></strong>. Click the link below to set your password and access your account.</p>

<p><%= link_to "Accept Invitation & Set Password", invitation_url(@token) %></p>

<p>This link expires in 7 days. Once you set your password, the link will no longer work.</p>

<p>If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<hr>

<p>Have questions? Just reply to this email.</p>
